column5: Might be a stupid question but is there a n ice road from wheelers point to youngs bay camp for pickup trucks. Thanks
I am pretty sure that is a no. There was an ice road from Springsteel near Warroad the last couple of years, but not this year. Too expensive to maintain.
I was at the northwest angel last Friday and drove from the northwest angel to Kenora on the ice road Pretty cool experience.
I have that on my list to do. I have heard it is a great drive!
